column5: Hi  I'm on a quest for Activate Gel Walleye, has anyone seen it in the GTA or Eastern Ontario?  RSVP via PM - SVP  David  aka  Superdad
We have only one of the spray in stock left at Fishing World and have ordered the gel and it should be in in the next few weeks.  We could order a special order for ya if ya need it asap.
What`s this a new aftershave or something???

I have not yet tried the gel,but i use the spray for walleyes & salmon all the time david !!! and it really works well,and stays on the bait for quite a while,mustad knew what they were doing when they made that stuff for sure !!!...cheers
Hey David, we picked it up at BassProShops this past Sunday.
